OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FStarting fine and dry with
OL,6,Flittle cloud and light winds. By the
OL,7,Fafternoon some patchy cloud will
OL,8,Fdevelop, and there is a low risk of
OL,9,Fisolated thunderstorms in the
OL,10,Fafternoon. Some brisk easterly winds
OL,11,Fdeveloping, feeling cooler along the
OL,12,Fcoast.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FDry, with cloud building
OL,15,Fthrough the evening. Some low cloud
OL,16,Fmay spread in from the coast later in
OL,17,Fthe night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
